---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import Background from "../components/Background.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import AnimatedText from "../components/AnimatedText.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Back from "@components/Back.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
    <Icon class="absolute h-[1300px] right-[-70px]" name="wigle" />
    <Icon class="absolute h-[1300px] bottom-0 left-[-70px]" name="wigle2" />

    <Background>
        <div class="max-w-7xl m-auto px-7">
            <h1 class="gradient-text text-2xl font-bold">About</h1>
            <div class="max-w-5xl m-auto mt-10 lg:mt-20">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:items-end">
                        <p class="max-w-md text-md font-medium">
                            <AnimatedText>
                                My journey began with <span
                                    class="text-secondary"
                                    >game development</span
                                >, where I honed my skills in creating
                                captivating experiences using <span
                                    class="text-secondary">Game Maker</span
                                > and <span class="text-secondary">Unity</span>,
                                utilizing both Game Maker Script and visual
                                coding. This foundation allowed me to grasp the
                                fundamentals of software development and sparked
                                my curiosity for more.
                            </AnimatedText>
                        </p>
                        <Icon class="mt-10" width="90" name="unity" />
                    </div>
                    <Icon
                        class="m-auto mt-6 lg:mt-0"
                        width="270"
                        name="gamemaker"
                    />
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row justify-between mt-10"
                >
                    <Icon
                        class="m-auto mt-5 lg:mt-10"
                        width="110"
                        name="java"
                    />
                    <p class="max-w-lg text-right text-md font-medium">
                        <AnimatedText>
                            As I delved further into the realm of programming, I
                            transitioned to building console applications using
                            <span class="text-secondary">Java</span> and <span
                                class="text-secondary">C++</span
                            >. This foray exposed me to the intricacies of
                            creating robust and efficient software, shaping my
                            problem-solving abilities and attention to detail.
                        </AnimatedText>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <Icon width="115" class="m-auto my-10" name="cpp" />
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 lg:gap-24">
                    <div class="lg:mt-12">
                        <p class="max-w-xl text-md font-medium">
                            <AnimatedText>
                                Driven by a desire to expand my horizons, I
                                ventured into the realm of <span
                                    class="text-secondary">web development</span
                                > and <span class="text-secondary">UI</span> design.
                                Crafting visually appealing and user-friendly websites
                                became my forte as I leveraged my understanding of
                                <span class="text-secondary">front-end</span> technologies
                                and delved into the world of <span
                                    class="text-secondary">back-end</span
                                > development. This exploration led me to develop
                                <span class="text-secondary"
                                    >content management systems</span
                                > (CMSs) and <span class="text-secondary"
                                    >microservices</span
                                >, empowering businesses to deliver dynamic and
                                scalable <span class="text-secondary">web</span>
                                solutions.
                            </AnimatedText>
                        </p>
                        <div
                            class="lg:ml-20 mt-12 lg:mt-0 flex gap-10 lg:gap-0 justify-center lg:justify-between"
                        >
                            <Icon width="50" name="rabbitmq" />
                            <Icon class="lg:mt-24" width="115" name="oauth" />
                            <Icon class="lg:mt-12" width="83" name="js" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="flex flex-row lg:flex-col justify-center lg:justify-normal flex-1 gap-10"
                    >
                        <Icon width="64" name="figma" />
                        <Icon
                            class="self-center lg:ml-20"
                            width="90"
                            name="css"
                        />
                        <Icon
                            class="lg:ml-8 lg:mt-12"
                            width="92"
                            name="react"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex justify-center gap-10 lg:gap-0 lg:justify-between h-48 lg:ml-10 lg:mr-20"
                >
                    <Icon width="195" name="nodejs" />
                    <Icon class="lg:self-end lg:mr-11" width="90" name="go" />
                    <Icon
                        class="lg:self-start hidden lg:block"
                        width="105"
                        name="mysql"
                    />
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center lg:flex-row justify-between lg:mt-20"
                >
                    <Icon class="mt-12 lg:mt-28 ml-4" width="150" name="rust" />
                    <p class="flex-1 max-w-2xl text-right text-md font-medium">
                        <AnimatedText>
                            During my high school years, my fascination with the
                            inner workings of systems and the intricacies of
                            <span class="text-secondary">compilers</span> ignited.
                            I embarked on creating streaming parsers using <span
                                class="text-secondary">TypeScript</span
                            >
                            and <span class="text-secondary">Rust</span>,
                            pushing the boundaries of data processing
                            efficiency. Additionally, I delved into the realm of
                            <span class="text-secondary">database</span> engines,
                            further expanding my knowledge of <span
                                class="text-secondary"
                                >system-level programming</span
                            >.
                        </AnimatedText>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="flex justify-center gap-10 lg:justify-between max-w-md m-auto mt-12"
                >
                    <Icon class="lg:mt-12" width="86" name="ts" />
                    <Icon width="111" name="sql" />
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row mt-12 justify-between">
                    <p class="max-w-lg text-md font-medium">
                        <AnimatedText>
                            In pursuit of pushing my skills to the limit, I
                            undertook a challenging endeavor for my finalsâ€”a
                            personal programming language built entirely from
                            scratch. This ambitious project involved developing
                            a <span class="text-secondary">just-in-time</span> (JIT)
                            compiler and building a seamless <span
                                class="text-secondary"
                                >foreign function interface</span
                            >
                            (FFI), showcasing my dedication to exploring cutting-edge
                            concepts and embracing the art of <span
                                class="text-secondary">language design</span
                            >.
                        </AnimatedText>
                    </p>
                    <Icon
                        class="mt-12 self-center lg:mt-32 lg:mr-28"
                        width="150"
                        name="ot"
                    />
                </div>
                <p class="mt-20 lg:mt-40 text-md font-medium">
                    <AnimatedText>
                        Throughout my journey, I've developed a versatile skill
                        set, combining my expertise in game development, web
                        technologies, system-level programming, and compiler
                        design. This amalgamation allows me to approach projects
                        from multiple angles, adapting to the unique
                        requirements of each endeavor.
                    </AnimatedText>
                </p>
                <p class="mt-10 lg:mt-20 text-md font-medium">
                    <AnimatedText>
                        I'm excited to share my knowledge, experiences, and
                        creations with you through this website. Whether you're
                        seeking consultation, collaboration, or simply exploring
                        the possibilities of software development, I'm here to
                        assist you in transforming ideas into reality.
                    </AnimatedText>
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-center my-16">
                    My current favourite technologies
                </h2>
                <div class="flex max-w-lg gap-5 justify-between m-auto mb-20">
                    <Icon width="121" name="rust" />
                    <Icon width="92" name="deno" />
                    <Icon width="87" name="tailwind" />
                    <Icon width="80" name="astro" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <Footer />
    </Background>
</Layout>

<style>
    svg {
        transition: transform 0.4s;
    }
    svg:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }
</style>
